Package: paradox
Type: Package
Title: Define and Work with Parameter Spaces for Complex Algorithms
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jakob", "Richter", NULL, "code@jakob-r.de", role = c("cre", "aut")),
    person("Xudong", "Sun", NULL, "smilesun.east@gmail.com", role = c("aut")),
    person("Michel", "Lang", NULL, "michellang@gmail.com", role = c("aut")),
    person("Bernd", "Bischl", NULL, "bernd_bischl@gmx.net", role = c("aut"))
    )
Description:
  Easily define parameter spaces, constraints and dependencies for
  arbitrary algorithms, to program on such spaces.
  Statistical designs and random samplers can be constructed.
  paradox is a successor of the 'ParamHelpers' package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/mlr-org/paradox
BugReports: https://github.com/mlr-org/paradox/issues
NeedsCompilation: no
Depends:
    data.table
